Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core

Class AnimatedArchitectureSpigotPlatform

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core.AnimatedArchitectureSpigotPlatform
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAnimatedArchitecturePlatform
@Singleton public final class AnimatedArchitectureSpigotPlatform extends Object implements IAnimatedArchitecturePlatform
The main class of the Animated Architecture Spigot plugin.

This class is responsible for initializing the various components of the plugin and to provide access to them for external plugins. Internally, this plugin uses dependency injection and as such does not use the getters provided by this class.

Refer to nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core for more information on how to obtain the instance of this class.
